name: Vintage navy grab bag with bamboo handles
description:
Navy grab bag with bamboo handles. Vintage - I think it's probably 1980s but the styles is more like 50s or 60s. Made by Marks and Spencer.

It's made from a synthetic waterproof leather-look material. There are two compartments in the bag plus a zip up pocket for valuables. Bag is big enough to carry large books. Fastens with two magnetic clips.

Excellent condition. Measures 13x11 inches and is 4 inches deep.

Item will be posted wrapped in tissue paper. Please let me know if you are buying this as a gift and I will happily include a message and gift wrap it for you.

Any questions, please get in touch!

name: Set of 3 bone china vintage plates with pink flowers
description:
Set of 3 plates with pink flowers and gold edging. 1950s - made in England. Measures 6 inches across. On the bottom of each plate it says "Crown Royal, bone china made in England".

Plates have some surface scratches and marks and the edging has faded in some places, would still be fabulous for serving cupcakes on.

Item will be posted well wrapped in bubble wrap and tissue paper. I used recycled packaging. Please let me know if you are buying this as a gift and I will happily include a message and gift wrap it for you.

Any questions, please get in touch!
